name: HER MAJESTY'S PRINT
description:
/// LIMITED EDITION VOIX DE VILLIA SCARF ///

65 cm x 65 cm
Silk Crepe de Chine Fabric.

Designed, digitally printed and constructed in Australia. All designs use the original Victorian elevations and sections of Her Majesty's Theatre, a cultural hub once located on Pitt street in Sydney. 

2 SCARVES AVAILABLE.

Please allow 1-2 weeks for shipping in Australia / 2-3 weeks internationally. 

www.veronika-veil.com
